lead_paragraph: New head coach Francesco Guidolin has lifted the mood at Swansea City with the players keen to prove their worth to the Italian, captain Ashley Williams said after Sunday's 2-1 Premier League win over Everton.

headline.print_headline: Guidolin Has Lifted the Mood at Swansea, Says Williams
